modName: MW - Dunmer - Gondolier's Inspired Mod of Setvi - Skyrim
summary:
Add renamed clothes inspired by the MW Gondolier's of Vivec.
You can find the renamed clothes in a Gondolier Knapsack at the New Gnisis Cornerclub of Windhelm.
You can enchant them.
Mod I've done for personal use, I choose to share it with you, maybe it can help.
Sorry for my bad English.
descriptionHtml:
[color=#efefef][size=4][b][center]Add renamed clothes inspired by the MW Gondolier's of Vivec.

You can find the renamed clothes in a Gondolier Knapsack at the New Gnisis Cornerclub of Windhelm.

You can enchant them.

Mod I've done for personal use, I choose to share it with you, maybe it can help.

Sorry for my bad English.

Since I start in a new job, I've no time to mod/update/play Skyrim.

No DLC or anything required.

Thanks, Setvi.

My others mods:
